Karana Chapter</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzatrizspiritscale.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zatriz Spiritscale</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Pippified Lizard King</span><br>  Posts: 143<br> <font color=#8E9173>(5/25/01 1:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=120.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Raid Enforcer</span><hr size=1> I'll nominate Stonescale as the Raid Enforcer.  In fact, I think he'd like it.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><hr>
